Preconditions:
The weights array must not be null.
The weights array must contain at least one element.
The days parameter must be a positive integer.

Postconditions:
The returned weight capacity must be an integer.
The returned weight capacity must be the least possible weight capacity that will result in all packages being shipped within the specified number of days.
All packages on the conveyor belt must be shipped within the specified number of days using the returned weight capacity.